# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
backend/.venv-test/

# Production TLS material — never commit (Phase 11).
# Track only the README + layout templates; the real origin.crt /
# deploy/ is no longer in this repo — nginx + TLS terminate at a
# standalone edge proxy stack (see docker-compose.prod.yml header).

# Backup files dumped by the backend into the bind-mounted host folder.
# Keep the README so the directory survives a fresh clone.
backups-host/*
!backups-host/README.txt
